Package: FBC
Type: Package
Title: Full Bayesian Calibration
Version: 1.0
Author: Parham Pishrobat
Maintainer: The package maintainer <par.pishrobat@ubc.ca>
Description: FBC provides employs a Full Bayesian Calibration method to calibrate the simulator 
             model using both field observations and simulator outputs. It is based on Kennedy and 
             O'Hagan (2001) calibration model and used Metropolis-Within Gibbs MCMC algorithm with 
             adaptive proposal.
